value.0: This half-elven woman presents a powerful, intimidating front, that leaves no question of her authority.
This elf seems to be blushing, probably because of his friends joking about his encounter with the sirines.
There is nothing pleasant about the smile on this ranger's face. Malevolent hatred is the only description that could fit.
Strange runes and pictographs, likely arcane in nature, have been scorched into the sides of this hide-covered strongbox.
Thick metal bands encircle the barrel-planks, ensuring a tight seal.
